00:22:01.846 --> 00:22:04.379
<i>Son of Ruth and Willard McGill.
Charles was born and raised</i>

183
00:22:04.381 --> 00:22:06.581
<i>in Cicero. Illinois. outside Chicago.</i>

184
00:22:06.583 --> 00:22:09.542
<i>Charles graduated valedictorian
from Francis Xavier High School</i>

185
00:22:09.544 --> 00:22:10.885
<i>at the age of 14.</i>

186
00:22:10.887 --> 00:22:14.150
