Charles led the debate team

190
00:22:23.717 --> 00:22:25.717
to national championship
three years running

191
00:22:25.719 --> 00:22:27.204
and won the Larkin Prize.

192
00:22:27.587 --> 00:22:29.321
<i>He was Editor-in-Chief of the Law Review</i>

193
