00:22:32.559 --> 00:22:35.327
<i>where he went on to graduate
magna cum laude.</i>

196
00:22:35.329 --> 00:22:37.930
<i>After clerking at both
the Delaware Court of Chancery</i>

197
00:22:37.932 --> 00:22:40.899
<i>and the United States Court of
Appeals for the Tenth Circuit.</i>

198
00:22:40.901 --> 00:22:44.302
